newsitem.title: USA: Indosat at 30-7/8 in New York on Monday.
newsitem.headline: Indosat at 30-7/8 in New York on Monday.

text.p: PT Indonesian Satellite Corporation (Indosat) closed at 30-7/8 in New York on Monday. It recorded the day's low of 30-7/8 and the day's high of 31-1/8.
Volume was 97,500 American Depository Shares. Block volume was 53,000. Its previous close on Friday was 31.
